---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Services"
  description="Central Coast Windows offers thermally broken aluminium window supply, residential installation, and custom design consultation across Sydney, Central Coast, and Newcastle."
  currentPage="services"
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <section style="padding: 80px 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">What We Offer</p>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Our Services</h1>
      <p class="section-sub">From initial consultation through to final installation, we handle the full process. No handoffs, no confusion — just one team that knows windows.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service 1: Supply -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154526-990dced4db0d?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Thermally broken aluminium window frames"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">01</span>
          <h2>Thermally Broken Window Supply</h2>
          <p>We supply premium thermally broken aluminium windows engineered to eliminate heat transfer and cold bridging. Every unit we supply meets Australian energy performance standards and is designed to deliver year-round comfort without compromising on aesthetics.</p>
          <p>Our windows feature a high-performance polyamide thermal break within the aluminium frame — a non-conductive barrier that stops heat from moving through the frame. Combined with the right glass specification, they deliver dramatically improved U-values compared to standard aluminium.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <h3>What's Included</h3>
            <p>Full product specification, frame profiles, glass configuration selection, colour and finish options, and delivery coordination to your site or our installation crew.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top: 24px">
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7"><strong style="color: var(--text)">Available finishes:</strong> Powder-coated in a full range of colours including standard whites, blacks, greys, and custom colours on request.</p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 8px"><strong style="color: var(--text)">Glass options:</strong> Double glazing, laminated, tinted, low-e coatings — we'll help you select based on orientation, performance goals, and budget.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2: Installation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Professional window installation"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">02</span>
          <h2>Residential Installation</h2>
          <p>Our installation team fits thermally broken windows directly into your home with a precision, draught-free finish. Whether you're replacing a single window or upgrading your entire home, we manage the process from removal through to completion.</p>
          <p>We work with homeowners undertaking renovations as well as builders working on new constructions. Coordination is simple — we show up, we do the work properly, and we leave the site clean.</p>

          <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏠</div>
              <h3>Single Room Upgrades</h3>
              <p>Replacing one or two windows? We handle small jobs with the same care as full homes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
              <h3>Full-Home Replacements</h3>
              <p>Complete window upgrades coordinated efficiently to minimise disruption to your household.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🔨</div>
              <h3>New Build Supply & Fit</h3>
              <p>Working with a builder? We supply and install to specification, on schedule.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 3: Consultation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565538810643-b5bdb714032a?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Window design consultation"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">03</span>
          <h2>Custom Design & Consultation</h2>
          <p>Not sure where to start? That's what we're here for. Our consultation process helps you understand your options across frame profiles, glass specifications, opening types, and finishes — all balanced against your energy performance goals, building codes, and personal style.</p>
          <p>There's no one-size-fits-all answer in window selection. A north-facing living room needs a different solution to a west-facing bedroom. We help you make the right call for each opening.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <h3>What to Expect</h3>
            <p>A no-pressure conversation about your project. We'll assess your existing setup, discuss your goals, recommend the right products, and provide a clear quote. No jargon, no upselling — just honest advice from someone who knows the product.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-section">
    <p class="section-label">Get Started</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Ready for a Quote?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Tell us about your project and we'll come back to you quickly with a clear, no-obligation quote.</p>
    <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/science" class="btn-outline">Learn How They Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
